                     <interp inst="t18050529-9-off51" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18050529-9-off51" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18050529-9-cd52" type="crimeDate">13th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18050529-9-off51 t18050529-9-cd52"></join>, four pounds eight ounces weight of pewter, value 3 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18050529-9-victim113" type="victimName">
                     Peter 
